<paragraph id="8400A579FFD6FF9ADE8DF852FC21F782" blockId="3.[136,933,2028,2051]" box="[136,933,2028,2051]" pageId="3" pageNumber="86">
<emphasis id="B6CB796BFFD6FF9ADE8DF852FF73F781" bold="true" box="[136,247,2028,2050]" pageId="3" pageNumber="86">FIGURE 2</emphasis>
. The new species 
